      ZUMUDIUMUGIUHUIAIZJZUHUIBIZJZLZDKURDKZUTDKZLULUPURUTDMUKVADUKUHUQUSLZJVAU
      JVDUHUIABNOUHUQUSPQRUNVBUOVCDUMASDUMBSTUADUMUCSUMUEUFNUAUB $.
      $( [20-Aug-93] $)

    $( The class union of the intersection of two classes.  Exercise 4.12(n)
