  ${
    $d x y A $.  $d x y B $.  $d x y C $.  $( ` x y ` are dummy. $)
    $( Subclass relationship for class union.  Theorem 61 of [Suppes] p. 39. $)
    uniss $p |- ( A (_ B -> U. A (_ U. B ) $=
      ( vx vy wss wel cv wcel wa wex cab cuni wi wal ssel imland 19.22dv
