  $( The Axiom of Union and its converse.  A class is a set iff its union is a
     set. $)
  uniexb $p |- ( A e. V <-> U. A e. V ) $=
    ( cvv wcel cuni uniexg cpw wss pwuni wi pwexg ssexg syl mpi impbi ) ABCZADZ
    BCZABEQAPFZGZOAHQRBCSOIPBJARBKLMN $.
